{"tid":752483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工作壓力不開心 女子廁所上吊昏迷","createTime":"2018-07-23T00:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T06:24:46.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b3640096088d3a2bac46009806ee34761beace","tid":752483,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T00:36:42.000Z","msg":"慈雲山翠鳳街35寶翠大廈一單位，凌晨1時許，一名23歲姓黃女子，在住所廁所內以衣物上吊，昏迷不醒，姓梁31歲男友人稍後發現報警，救護員將女子送院廣華醫院搶救後，命危留醫救治。<br />\n<br />\n警員在屋內展開調查，現場並無遺書，初步相信女事主因工作問題困擾，並曾向家人透露表示不開心，加上經常與男友爭吵，案件並無可疑。據悉，女事主早前曾企圖自殺不逐。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180723/58474285\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58474285&d=36Rt6SDeh3uDv2hevI%2BaV54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5a7f8645\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180723%2F58474285&h=c3c36ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180723/58474285</a>"},{"pid":"468ca3a9ea663bcaaaadecb21362bb9910a479d8","tid":752483,"uid":164913,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2344b216e611f7a1957e6a2b6e5adf42b7489146","tid":752483,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:07:32.000Z","msg":"廿三歲... rip"},{"pid":"aba30c7ce96c2a0eb9ec753a2b6df42a73c8a464","tid":752483,"uid":76135,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2344b216e611f7a1957e6a2b6e5adf42b7489146","tid":752483,"uid":30604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T01:07:32.000Z","msg":"廿三歲... rip"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018